1. 获取多维index数据
                       Total
       Country               
bronze France           475.0
       Germany          454.0
       Soviet Union     584.0
       United Kingdom   505.0
       United States   1052.0
gold   Germany          407.0
       Italy            460.0
       Soviet Union     838.0
       United Kingdom   498.0
       United States   2088.0
silver France           461.0
       Italy            394.0
       Soviet Union     627.0
       United Kingdom   591.0
       United States   1195.0

获取United Kingdom的数据
# Create alias for pd.IndexSlice: idx
idx = pd.IndexSlice
# Print all the data on medals won by the United Kingdom
print(medals_sorted.loc[idx[:,'United Kingdom'],:])

2.拼接方向
row方向拼接index会重复,需要使用reset_index或者concat需要使用参数
columns方向拼接index相同会合并如下
In [1]: bronze.head()
Out[1]: 
                 Total
Country               
United States   1052.0
Soviet Union     584.0
United Kingdom   505.0
France           475.0
Germany          454.0

In [2]: silver.head()
Out[2]: 
                 Total
Country               
United States   1195.0
Soviet Union     627.0
United Kingdom   591.0
France           461.0
Italy            394.0

# Concatenate medal_list horizontally using an inner join: medals
        medals = pd.concat(medal_list,keys=['bronze', 'silver', 'gold'],axis=1)
        
        # Print medals
        print(medals)
                bronze  silver    gold
                 Total   Total   Total
France           475.0   461.0     NaN
Germany          454.0     NaN   407.0
Italy              NaN   394.0   460.0
Soviet Union     584.0   627.0   838.0
United Kingdom   505.0   591.0   498.0
United States   1052.0  1195.0  2088.0

默认是外连接
如果使用内连接得到如下结果,必须index都存在在三个DF中才留下
medals = pd.concat(medal_list,keys=['bronze', 'silver', 'gold'],axis=1,join='inner')
        
        # Print medals
        print(medals)
                bronze  silver    gold
                 Total   Total   Total
Country                               
United States   1052.0  1195.0  2088.0
Soviet Union     584.0   627.0   838.0
United Kingdom   505.0   591.0   498.0

3.numpy的方法

numpy类型合并
np.hstack([b,a])                    横向合并
np.concatenate([b,a],axis=1)        横向合并

np.vstack([a,c])                    纵向合并
np.concatenate([b,a],axis=0)        纵向合并

可以通过np.array(dataframe)转换dataframe到nparray

